        <!-- Product Details Section -->
        <section class="product-details-section">
          
          <!-- Stone Preview Image - absolutely positioned top-right -->
          <div class="stone-preview-img">
            <img src="../../../../assets/img/NS/Natural Stones Tiles/Mint.png" alt="Mint Sandstone" class="img-fluid">
          </div>
<div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12">
                <div class="product-intro-text">
                  <h1 class="product-title" data-aos="fade-up">Mint Sandstone</h1>

                  <div class="product-description" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                  <p>A cool, mint-hued sandstone with a soothing palette, ideal for swimming pool surrounds and garden features. This stone is sourced from trusted quarries and selected for consistent colour, texture, and natural character. It performs well in both interior and exterior applications, including flooring, wall cladding, pathways, patios, and landscape elements. With proper sealing and routine care, it retains its beauty for years and handles daily wear with ease. Available in multiple finishes and edge profiles, it can be customized to suit contemporary as well as traditional design concepts. From homes to commercial projects, it offers a practical and elegant surface solution with timeless appeal.</p>
                  
                  <p>Its consistent pale-green tones pair beautifully with water features and lush landscapes, creating serene outdoor environments.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            
